  sourcePage 3
obj_root_law_sections_3_content:
  string
  line 3
  line `and with such vouchers as the Governor or Governor in Council, or Lieutenant Governor, shall from time`
  line order.
  line `XIV. The Governor or Governor in Council, or Lieutenant Governor may, at any time, suspend the`
  line `operation of this Act in any town or Suburb, and appoint any person or persons to examine and report upon`
  line `the behavior of the Commissioners, or any of them, or their Officers in the execution of this Act.`
  line __________
obj_root_law_sections_3_footnotes:
  string
  line
